<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_03_IH_0006</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema611_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_03_ih_0006 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star2" lang="y">어떤 수를 7로 나누어야 할 것을 잘못하여 곱했더니 63이 되었습니다. 옳게 계산한 값을 분수로 나타내려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">어떤 수를 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center mt_30">
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p><span lang="y">어떤 수를 </span><span class="nemo"></span><span lang="y">라 하면 </span><span class="nemo"></span><span lang="y">×7=63이므로</span> <span class="nemo"></span><span lang="y">=63÷7=9입니다</span></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">옳게 계산한 값을 분수로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center mt_30">
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="1(2)/(7)(=(9)/(7))" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <div class="flex gap_0 align_center">
                    <span lang="y">옳게 계산하면 9÷7=입니다.</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>9</span><span>7</span></div>
                    =
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>7</span></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
